casebody.data:
Wisniewski, Appellant, v. Wisniewski, Appellee.

[Cite as Wisniewski v. Wisniewski (1985), 20 Ohio St. 3d 20.]

(No. 85-823 Decided October 30, 1985.) Frank W. Cubbon, Jr. & Associates Co., L.P.A., and Darrel L. Rice, for appellant. Neipp & Wingart Co., L.P.A., and William H. Bracy, for appellee.

This cause on appeal from the court of appeals (case No. L-84-414) is *21sua sponte reversed on authority of Shearer v. Shearer (1985), 18 Ohio St. 3d 94, and Kirchner v. Crystal (1984), 15 Ohio St. 3d 326.

Celebrezze, C.J., Sweeney, C. Brown, Douglas and Wright, JJ., concur. Locher, J., dissents. Holmes, J., not participating.
